    "summary": "As a senior indirect tax professional with over 15 years of experience working with global companies in EMEA and APAC, I have gained extensive expertise in developing and leveraging a tax function and tax technology to support organizational changes, business initiatives, and growth. I am also experienced in providing high-level tax technology strategic advice to organizations, a skill not so common among tax professionals. My structured and solution-oriented approach, always with a bigger picture in mind, helps me consistently deliver honest and transparent results. \n\nMy career has a unique trajectory which I\u2019m very proud of \u2013 I started as a junior VAT compliance specialist and progressed to a senior global indirect tax managerial role, thanks to my self-teaching skills, proactivity, persistence, and people around me who recognized my ambition and helped me pursue it. \n\nMy main competencies include:\n\n\ud83d\udfe2\tIndirect Taxation\n\ud83d\udfe2\tValue-Added Tax (VAT)\n\ud83d\udfe2\tIndirect Tax Project Management\n\ud83d\udfe2\tVAT Compliance Strategy & Management\n\ud83d\udfe2\tTax Process Digitalization\n\ud83d\udfe2\tData Management\n\ud83d\udfe2\tTransaction Mapping\n\ud83d\udfe2\tTax Engine\n\ud83d\udfe2\tE-invoicing Strategy\n\ud83d\udfe2\tReporting Tool\n\ud83d\udfe2\tTax Control Framework\n\ud83d\udfe2\tSupply Chain Management\n\ud83d\udfe2\tTax Authorities Relationship\n\ud83d\udfe2\tTeam Leadership\n\ud83d\udfe2\tTraining & Coaching\n\nI also like to explore outside of my comfort zone, give myself stretch assignments, and do whatever it takes to learn and grow as a person and professional. I am committed to self-improvement and always seek opportunities to grow and develop my skills.\n\nLooking forward to connecting with you!",
